{"tid":1568591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家決定係最大贏面時宣布退出？","createTime":"2019-09-14T10:22:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T10:59:05.000Z","uid":278538,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"5e52b11b75262ee8503182106c57d0b3d2b37b46","tid":1568591,"uid":278538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:22:55.000Z","msg":"當大家「歌舞昇平」嘅時候，<br />\n有無留意中美關係已經緩和左好多？<br />\n<br />\n美國已經打算同中國簽定臨時貿易協議，<br />\n同時亦有議員表示不支持《香港人權民主法案》。<br />\n<br />\n繼續「歌舞昇平」係外媒眼中只係等於傳遞緊<br />\n1. 林鄭撤回，香港人收貨<br />\n2. 香港已經變返民主自由<br />\n3. 最緊要都係同大陸關係搞掂攞盡著數<br />\n<br />\n如果真係覺得已經贏左，<br />\n我無嘢好講。<br />\n如果唔係，<br />\n諗一諗而家條路點走。<br />\n政府已經完全隱形，<br />\n由得人民打人民，<br />\n出動國旗黨轉移焦點。<br />\n無人想重複2014嘅錯誤。<br />\n<br />\n利申，<br />\n隻歌我堅鐘意，<br />\n但，<br />\n型，係好型<br />\n聽，係好聽<br />\n但好型好聽會贏到嗎？<br />\n美國國會會希望一隻歌而感動嗎？"},{"pid":"d4eb18021a91f0ead14b0de20664513abc312638","tid":1568591,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:25:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"67058d58a5c17c738b5245a3d4ba7d698aea8ede","tid":1568591,"uid":102491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:26:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a478c5e9777928eda46b0d207672a5878500073","tid":1568591,"uid":14303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:35:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1c31d1bb145cc6dd0a4a4e601519d067bf34030e","tid":1568591,"uid":257422,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:36:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母呀！<br />\n死差佬同藍絲又周圍打人！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"> 聽日九月十五日<br />\n<br />\n2pm<br />\n 銅鑼灣東角道 /<br />\n維園 / 英領 </span> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全人類同我出黎！<br />\n[red] 唔係我屌埋你老母呀！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.kym-cdn.com/photos/images/newsfeed/000/915/652/b49.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.kym-